title: Lenovo ThinkCentre E50-00 Intel® Pentium® J2900 4 GB DDR3-SDRAM 1 TB HDD FreeDOS Mini Tower PC Black
description:
Lenovo ThinkCentre E50-00 Intel® Pentium® J2900 4 GB DDR3-SDRAM 1 TB HDD FreeDOS Mini Tower PC Black


Cost-Effective Processing. The Lenovo E50-00 supports up to an Intel® Pentium® quad-core processor, so you can have the power and productivity of Intel® inside without breaking the bank. Windows 8.1 Preloaded Start using the Lenovo E50-00 right out of the box — it comes preloaded with Windows 8.1 with Bing. Windows 8.1 Pro and Windows 7 are also available. Stylish, Understated Design From its hidden air inlets to its conveniently placed input/output ports, from its well-situated top handle to its asset tag mark, the E50-00 is efficient to use — and looks great. Power-Saving External Adapter The Lenovo E50-00’s external adapter saves power – and money — when compared to typical internal adapters. It's a 90/65W unit and it results in up to 35% power savings compared to traditional PSUs. Fast USB Connection Move data between the E50-00 and other devices quickly with USB 3.0 — it's up to 10 times faster than previous USB technologies, and is backward-compatible. Discrete Graphics Support For impressive visuals, choose a model with discrete graphics — up to an AMD R5 235 1G graphics card is available. Cost-Saving Power Manager Power Manager helps users adjust power settings to achieve the best balance between system performance and power saving. Easy Maintenance You'll always have peace of mind with the E50-00: Lenovo's One-Key® Rescue System makes bouncing back from a crash or virus a snap.

description:
ASUS M 31AD-_001S Intel® Core™ i3 i3-4130 4 GB DDR3-SDRAM 1 TB HDD NVIDIA® GeForce® GT 620 Windows 8.1 Tower PC Black


Experience Multimedia in Style - Windows 8.1 or other editions available - Powered by the latest 4th generation Intel® Core™ processors - ASUS Smart Cooling technology lowers operating temperatures by up to 11.4℃ - Front USB 3.0 ports with Ai Charger technology for rapid recharging of mobile devices Experience Multimedia in Style With brush-finished surfaces, a spun-metallic power button and cleverly-hidden HDD bay, the M31AD complements your style. It is powered by a 4th generation Intel® Core™ processor, and features Full HD 1080p video playback for an immersive multimedia experience. Everyday Multimedia desktop PC leading in satisfaction with reliability* ASUS computers reflect a tradition of the finest quality, innovation and longevity. Based on the PCWorld USA 2012 reader survey of tech satisfaction, reliability, and service, users ranked ASUS as a leading choice for desktop PCs, citing high satisfaction with their value, connectivity, ease of use and reliability. The survey also found ASUS desktop PCs were one of the most likely to be recommended to others. More speed, more power Powered by the 4th generation Intel® Core™ processor, the M31AD features Intel® Turbo Boost Technology 2.0 that enables processor cores to run faster than the base operating frequency. The Integrated Intel® GMA and Intel® Quick Sync video technology provides high definition graphics and a high-quality video playback experience to answer all your entertainment needs. HDMI for Hi-definition Enjoyment HDMI With Full HD 1080p support, you can immerse yourself in a cinematic experience and enter a spectacular world of colors by connecting to a HD monitor or TV with the HDMI™ port . Ai-Charger The ASUS M31AD is supported by the Ai-Charger which offers 50% faster charging speeds for all USB-compatible devices. ASUS WebStorage: Up to 100GB free space Share your pictures, music and movies with 100GB* free space for 1 year, wirelessly share your files across multiple devices. With a keyword search, you can find the relevant files in no time. Record and upload the important meeting notes with snap shots, and then access them on any devices. QuietCool Technology** ASUS’ exclusive Smart Cooling System and Q-Fan lower operation temperatures by up to 11.4℃ and adjusts CPU fan speeds according to system loading, enabling the M31AD to power through intensive tasks whilst maintaining stable, quiet, cool, and efficient performance. **Optional 2X Life Span High-quality components provide utmost durability, improved longevity and enhanced thermal performance thanks to 100% top-quality solid conductive polymer capacitors. The best motherboards in the world ASUS desktop PCs are built on the best motherboards available — and we should know, because we make them. We’ve sold 465 million motherboards since we first started making them over 24 years ago and our models won over 1,000 awards in 2012 alone. Stringent Quality Test All units have passed and exceeded rigorous vibration, noise, thermal shock, and drop tests, ensuring ASUS products exceed the industry standard.

title: DELL Inspiron 3647 Intel® Core™ i5 i5-4460S 4 GB DDR3-SDRAM 1 TB HDD NVIDIA® GeForce® 705 Windows 8.1 SFF PC Black
description:
DELL Inspiron 3647 Intel® Core™ i5 i5-4460S 4 GB DDR3-SDRAM 1 TB HDD NVIDIA® GeForce® 705 Windows 8.1 SFF PC Black


So small. So big on possibilities. Sleek space-saver: Streamline your space with a desktop that’s easy on the eyes. The attractive design with a smooth black surface fits in nicely anywhere in your home. It also frees up desk space to let you enjoy more elbowroom for picture frames, souvenirs, snacks, or whatever it is you like to have handy. Optional HD monitor: View videos or organize photos on the HD or Full HD display of your choice. Choose the screen size that best suits your needs with the added flexibility to upgrade to a second display or larger monitor later. Speedy, smooth and spacious Power player: Count on the same performance of a regular desktop in a smaller PC with the latest processing power – up to 4th Gen Intel Core i5 processors. Run multiple programs at once so you can work on your website, create presentations, make a movie or listen to music at the same time with less lag. Updated operating system: Navigate smoothly with the new, feature-rich Windows 8.1. Learn how to personalize your desktop with great new apps and features that make multitasking a breeze. Windows 7 options available on select Inspiron desktops. High-capacity hard drive: With up to 1 TB of space, you’ll have room for all your photos, videos and important documents. Features to keep you connected Connect easily to your devices with convenient accessibility to plenty of ports so you can link up your camera, console, HDTV and more. The Inspiron Small Desktop features multiple high-speed USB 3.0 ports, USB 2.0 ports, an 8-in-1 media card reader and a VGA output. Connect to an HDTV through the HDMI port, or enjoy crystal clear audio through three audio jacks that support 5.1 surround sound. Your Inspiron Small Desktop comes with two port configurations. Fewer ports, greater affordability: Plug in your camera, charge your phone and still have room for additional devices. This affordable Inspiron Small Desktop configuration comes with one high-speed USB 3.0 port and four USB 2.0 ports. More ports, greater connectivity: With six USB 2.0 ports and two high-speed USB 3.0 ports, easily keep all your devices connected at once. This upgraded Inspiron Small Desktop configuration packs more ports for more connectivity. Dell is serious about your privacy Worried about Superfish? Dell limits its pre-loaded software to a small number of high-value applications on all of our computers. Each application we pre-load undergoes security, privacy and usability testing to ensure that our customers experience the best possible computing performance, faster set-up and reduced privacy and security concerns. Your content. Anywhere, anytime. Retrieve that document you forgot to take to the meeting. Access your photos. Collaborate on a project. With Dropbox, you can easily access all of your content anywhere. Dropbox Put your stuff in Dropbox and get to it from any device. Dropbox lets you edit docs, share photos, and show off videos from anywhere. Even if something happens to your PC, your stuff is always safe in Dropbox. Get 20GB of Dropbox space included for a year with your purchase of a new Dell PC.
